NK005(ca)009:0: dpal yang dag gi sgrub thabs bde chen thig le zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK005(ca)009:1: dpal he ru ka yang dag gi sgrub thabs bde chen thig le zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)009:2: bla ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:3: srid zhi kun gyi khyab bdag bde ba che //
NK005(ca)009:4: 'gyur med rdo rje bzhi yi rnam rol gyis //
NK005(ca)009:5: rtag tu dgyes rol dpal chen he ru ka /
NK005(ca)009:6: yang dag bla ma nyid la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)009:7: rnam dag 'od gsal gdod ma'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)009:8: rang rig he ru kar rdzogs de kho na'i //
NK005(ca)009:9: gnas lugs rnam pa'i lam gyis mtshon byed thabs //
NK005(ca)009:10: bde chen theg le mchog gi dpyid du spel //
NK005(ca)009:16: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba thob cing /
NK005(ca)009:17: thun mong dang khyad par gyi dam tshig la gnas pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:21: rjes kyi bya ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)009:23: dang po bya ba'i sngon 'gro ni /
NK005(ca)009:24: gnas khang legs par brgyan la /
NK005(ca)009:25: rten dang mchod gtor sogs mkho ba'i yo byad rnams bshams pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:26: gnyis pa rgyud sbyang ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:27: rang gi snying ga'i h'u gi 'od zer gyis bla
NK005(ca)009:28: ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK005(ca)009:29: lha tshogs thams cad badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs mkha' khyab
NK005(ca)009:31: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK005(ca)009:32: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:33: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK005(ca)009:34: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK005(ca)009:35: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK005(ca)009:36: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:37: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK005(ca)009:38: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK005(ca)009:39: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK005(ca)009:40: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK005(ca)009:41: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK005(ca)009:42: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK005(ca)009:43: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK005(ca)009:44: dag pa gsum gyi lus dbul lo //
NK005(ca)009:45: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK005(ca)009:46: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK005(ca)009:48: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus te /
NK005(ca)009:49: ka dag spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK005(ca)009:50: gsum pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:51: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las /
NK005(ca)009:52: h'u sh+r+ai badz+ra d+h+rikra h'u dzahzhesa brjod pas /
NK005(ca)009:53: rang nyid khro bo'i rgyal po zhe sdang rdo rje 'jigs su rung ba'i skur mos la /
NK005(ca)009:56: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK005(ca)009:57: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK005(ca)009:58: thams cad thugs rjes bskang zin gyis //
NK005(ca)009:59: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK005(ca)009:61: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:62: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK005(ca)009:63: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)009:64: zhes drag po'i tshams rngam dang bcas bskul bas /
NK005(ca)009:65: khro bo'i sprin phung sprul pa'i 'od zer 'khrug cing
NK005(ca)009:66: 'bar ba g.yas bskor du spros pas bgegs thams cad
NK005(ca)009:67: tshar bcad / slar g.yon bskor du 'dus pa las
NK005(ca)009:68: phyogs bcur khro bo chen po bcur gyur pa ni
NK005(ca)009:69: tshar bcad / / badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK005(ca)009:72: khro bo thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa smad
NK005(ca)009:73: phur bu 'bar bas bgegs la gzir zhing bsrung ba'i
NK005(ca)009:75: slar yang sna bug nas h'u ring por brjod pa'i
NK005(ca)009:76: sgra gdangs las mtshon cha lnga'i ye shes kyi 'od
NK005(ca)009:77: zer bskal pa'i me 'bar ba dang bcas pa spros
NK005(ca)009:78: / bgegs thams cad tshar bcad par mos la /
NK005(ca)009:87: badz+ra dz+wa la badz+ra h'u phata /
NK005(ca)009:89: slar 'dus pa las mtshon cha lnga'i ra gur gyis
NK005(ca)009:90: rim par dkrigs te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam
NK005(ca)009:92: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)009:93: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK005(ca)009:94: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK005(ca)009:95: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK005(ca)009:97: steng yang rdo rje'i bla re la //
NK005(ca)009:98: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi ste //
NK005(ca)009:99: phyogs mtshams rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK005(ca)009:100: rdo rje'i mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK005(ca)009:103: de bzhin du rdo rje'i gnas su /
NK005(ca)009:111: a ko ta ya mut+ga ra dang /
NK005(ca)009:113: zhes rim par gzhug cing so so'i rgya baca'o //
NK005(ca)009:114: de nas bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:116: mtshams bcad nang 'di tshun chad dang //
NK005(ca)009:117: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK005(ca)009:118: ci ste bka' las 'da' byed na //
NK005(ca)009:119: tho ba lcags kyur bcas pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:120: snying nas drangs te brdung bar bya //
NK005(ca)009:122: bzhi pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:123: bshags yul tshogs zhing ltar gsal btab la /
NK005(ca)009:124: ye shes sku mchog dang dam tshig nyer brgyad pa'am /
NK005(ca)009:126: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)009:127: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK005(ca)009:128: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs so sor smin //
NK005(ca)009:129: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos kyang //
NK005(ca)009:130: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK005(ca)009:131: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'ga' gyur pas //
NK005(ca)009:132: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK005(ca)009:133: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK005(ca)009:135: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:136: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK005(ca)009:137: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK005(ca)009:138: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK005(ca)009:139: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK005(ca)009:140: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)009:141: zhes lan gsum gyis dam bca' /
NK005(ca)009:142: drug pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:143: ye shes kyi 'khor lo mkha' khyab tu sad par bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:144: h+aum a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)009:145: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:146: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:147: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:148: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:149: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:150: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)009:152: byin chen byin phob dbang chen dbang bskur dngos grub mchog stsol bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:153: rol mo sna tshogs kyi sgra sbyar zhing /
NK005(ca)009:156: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs rnams bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la thim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:157: bdun pa mchod rdzas rlob pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:158: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros pas
NK005(ca)009:159: mchod rdzas kyi dngos 'dzin nyes skyon thams cad bsregs
NK005(ca)009:160: gtor bkrus te stong par gyur /
NK005(ca)009:162: bdud rtsi'i snod b+h+r+aum las b+hany+dza'i gzhal yas khang du
NK005(ca)009:163: nyi zla kha sbyor gyi dbus su bdud rtsi lnga
NK005(ca)009:165: rang gi mtheb srin nyi zla'i bar du rta mgrin
NK005(ca)009:166: yum bzhi dang bcas pas mtshan pa'i phyag rgya bdud
NK005(ca)009:168: +aahh+aum badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)009:170: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis bskul bas rta mgrin
NK005(ca)009:171: yum bzhi dang rol pa'i byang chub kyi sems dpa'
NK005(ca)009:173: ye shes kyi 'od zer 'bar bas bdud rtsir zhu
NK005(ca)009:174: zhing 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams cad bsdus nas
NK005(ca)009:175: 'khyil ba'i steng du +aahh+aum gis mtshan pa las slar
NK005(ca)009:177: snod bcud kyi dwangs ma bdud rtsir bsdus nas don gnyis byas te /
NK005(ca)009:178: 'bru gsum rta mgrin yum dang bcas pa 'od du zhu nas bdud rtsir 'khyil bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:179: gtor gzhong b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK005(ca)009:180: gtor rdzas las 'dod yon gyi phung por gyur /
NK005(ca)009:181: ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba la b+aa ge gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)009:183: 'dod yon drug gi lha mo 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK005(ca)009:184: bsam gyis mi khyab pa spro ba'i gter du bsam
NK005(ca)009:185: mo // b+h+r+aum b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)009:186: rak+ta'i zhal bu stong gsum dang mnyam pa'i nang du rak+ta la ra yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur /
NK005(ca)009:189: rang gi thugs ka'i 'od zer ra yig la phog
NK005(ca)009:190: pas 'od du 'bar bas dngos 'dzin sbyangs nas bdud
NK005(ca)009:192: gzar bu h+aum las skyes pa'i rdo rjes dkrugs pas
NK005(ca)009:193: rba rlabs dmar por zegs ma las 'dod yon gyi
NK005(ca)009:194: lha mo spro bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:196: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas mchod
NK005(ca)009:197: rdzas kyi ming yig dang po rnams 'phros 'dus pa
NK005(ca)009:198: las mchod rdzas rnams la thim par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)009:199: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK005(ca)009:201: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK005(ca)009:202: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK005(ca)009:205: mchod pa'i lha mo kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa'i
NK005(ca)009:206: sprin rab 'byams spro bas nam mkha' gang bar bsam
NK005(ca)009:207: mo // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la /
NK005(ca)009:208: ting 'dzin gsum gyi khog dbub pa /
NK005(ca)009:209: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK005(ca)009:210: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang gsum /
NK005(ca)009:213: bsam du med de sems nyid nam mkha' che //
NK005(ca)009:214: sems nyid nam mkha' bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK005(ca)009:215: bsam du med pa'i sems nyid nam mkha' ni //
NK005(ca)009:216: nam mkha'i mi dmigs par yang dmigs su med //
NK005(ca)009:218: zhes pas chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs spros pa dang bral ba'i stong pa nyid du bsgom pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:220: rang bzhin ye shes dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK005(ca)009:221: stong khams yongs la khyab pa'i thugs rje 'byung //
NK005(ca)009:222: sal ler gsal zhing phyogs med mtha' dang bral //
NK005(ca)009:223: dbyibs dang kha dog dngos med ye shes 'od //
NK005(ca)009:225: rang bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams byang chub la 'god par bya'o snyam pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:227: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid dag pa las //
NK005(ca)009:228: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge h+aum du gsal //
NK005(ca)009:229: bzung bas mi zin de phyir chu zla'i tshul //
NK005(ca)009:230: thig le'i dbyings nas rang byung sku ru gsal //
NK005(ca)009:232: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i rang rig h+aum yig 'bar bar gyur /
NK005(ca)009:234: zhes pas de nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog
NK005(ca)009:235: dkar po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa rgyan
NK005(ca)009:236: dang cha byad yongs su rdzogs pa nam mkhar gnas
NK005(ca)009:237: pa'i spyi bor / mgrin par +aah snying gar h+aum yig gis mtshan par bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:238: h+aum yig ring por bzhi brjod pas /
NK005(ca)009:239: 'bru gsum gyi 'od zer mthing dmar dkar ba khong
NK005(ca)009:240: brgyud du drangs nas sna rtser thon pa b+h+r+aum yig
NK005(ca)009:244: ye shes kyi 'od zer mkha' khyab tu spros te /
NK005(ca)009:245: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK005(ca)009:247: gzhi'i b+h+r+aum la thim pas nyi ma byed pa'i gzi brjid 'bar bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:249: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:250: brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)009:252: gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:254: e yam ram bam kem ram rnams chad /
NK005(ca)009:257: ra rak+ta dz+wa la sa mu dra /
NK005(ca)009:258: bam smin+ta dz+wa la man+da la /
NK005(ca)009:259: kem ni ri ti dz+wa la man+da la /
NK005(ca)009:261: zhes brjod pas rim pa bzhin /
NK005(ca)009:262: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK005(ca)009:263: 'thor byed rlung nag tshogs kyis rgya gram gtams //
NK005(ca)009:264: chags pa rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba klong 'khyil //
NK005(ca)009:265: zhing chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi mtha' dbus brdal //
NK005(ca)009:266: keng rus chen po brtsegs pa'i ri rab 'bar //
NK005(ca)009:267: ye shes 'bar ba'i me 'od kun tu 'phro //
NK005(ca)009:268: de dag kyang 'byung ba lnga dang /
NK005(ca)009:270: yum lnga'i mkha' klong gi rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:271: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dngos ni /
NK005(ca)009:272: gzhi'i b+h+r+aum yig ri rab kyi steng du chad pa 'od du zhu ba las /
NK005(ca)009:273: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra b+hany+dza dz+ny+aa na man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)009:275: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang /
NK005(ca)009:276: nang ma zla gam dmar nag sgo gcig pa /
NK005(ca)009:277: phyi bar khyams gru bzhi sgo bzhi sgo khyud rta bab dang bcas pa /
NK005(ca)009:278: tshar gsum thod pa'i rtsig pa rak+tasa sbyar zhing /
NK005(ca)009:279: gnam lcags urmo'i gzer gyis gtams pa /
NK005(ca)009:280: lha klu gza' skar zhing che chung la sogs pa'i ka gdung dang dral phyam byas pa /
NK005(ca)009:281: 'dod snam dang pha gus bskor zhing /
NK005(ca)009:289: bla bre la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)009:290: zhing chen gyi thog phubs dang ldan pa'i rtse mor tsit+ta dang /
NK005(ca)009:291: rdo rje'i tog gis spras shing /
NK005(ca)009:292: tshad dang mtshan nyid thams cad tshang ba pad+ma'i lte
NK005(ca)009:293: ba la gnas pa'i phyi nas dur khrod chen po
NK005(ca)009:294: brgyad / dur khrod kyi chos rnams kyis 'jigs par
NK005(ca)009:295: byas pa dang rdo rje'i ra ba ye shes kyi
NK005(ca)009:296: 'od zer bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar bas yongs su
NK005(ca)009:297: brgyad / bskor ba'o // pho brang gi dbus su
NK005(ca)009:298: rdo rje'i phreng bas zlum por bskor ba ru re'u
NK005(ca)009:299: mig cha dgur gyur pa'i lte bar zla gam kha
NK005(ca)009:300: brgyad / bskor ba'o // sprod dang / phyogs mtshams
NK005(ca)009:301: brgyad du zla gam logs nang du lta ba re
NK005(ca)009:303: gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:304: thugs ka nas zla gam dbus ma'i steng du /
NK005(ca)009:305: pam a ma bam rnams chad pa las /
NK005(ca)009:313: pad+ma zla nyi brtsegs pa'i gdan la dregs pa khyo shugs bsnol ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:316: zhes pas phyogs mtshams kyi zla gam brgyad la nyi
NK005(ca)009:317: ma'i dkyil 'khor zhing skam rlon zung re dang bcas
NK005(ca)009:318: pa'o // gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)009:319: dang po gtso bo bskyed pa la'ang /
NK005(ca)009:321: ye shes sems dpa' dbab pa /
NK005(ca)009:322: sku yongs rdzogs su bskyed pa dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)009:325: zhes glur blangs pas rim pa bzhin /
NK005(ca)009:326: rdo rje sems dpa' 'od du zhu nas h+aum yig tu gyur /
NK005(ca)009:327: de las h+aum gi sgra gdangs mkha' khyab tu spros 'dus pa las rdo rjer gyur /
NK005(ca)009:328: slar yang spro bsdu'i sbyor bas badz+ra he ru ka smug nag tshon gang bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:330: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta nam /
NK005(ca)009:335: sa ma ya ba ti nan /
NK005(ca)009:337: nam mkha'i he ru ka dbus kyi gdan steng du bzhugs pa la /
NK005(ca)009:338: nam mkha' gang ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis /
NK005(ca)009:339: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)009:340: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:341: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab las //
NK005(ca)009:342: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)009:343: de tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NK005(ca)009:344: shin tu khro gtum gdug par gyur //
NK005(ca)009:345: shin tu gdug cing khros pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:347: shin tu gdug cing khros pa la //
NK005(ca)009:348: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)009:349: shes rab thabs kyi rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)009:350: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)009:351: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:352: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
NK005(ca)009:353: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:354: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)009:355: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)009:356: dam tshig la sdang rnam spyod phyir //
NK005(ca)009:357: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK005(ca)009:362: dbang skur ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)009:364: he ru ka'i dam rgya smin mtshams su bcas te /
NK005(ca)009:365: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa gro d+h+ai shwa r+ai /
NK005(ca)009:366: sa ma ya de b+ai ta na sho d+ha ya ha na h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:367: ces pas 'bras bu'i he ru ka dpal chen po'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:368: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba chen po'i 'od zer can /
NK005(ca)009:369: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa /
NK005(ca)009:371: g.yon zhal dmar po gshe ba /
NK005(ca)009:372: dbus zhal mthing nag khros pa'i nyams can /
NK005(ca)009:373: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK005(ca)009:374: zhal gdams shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK005(ca)009:375: ljags 'dril la phata kyi rka na sgra sdeb cing /
NK005(ca)009:377: smin mtshams nas khro gnyer g.yo ba /
NK005(ca)009:378: sma ra dang smin ma'i glog 'od 'khyug cing /
NK005(ca)009:379: ral ba kham nag gyen du 'bar ba /
NK005(ca)009:380: nyi ma bye ba'i gzi mdangs can /
NK005(ca)009:381: sgeg pa la sogs pa gar gyi nyams dgus rgyas pa /
NK005(ca)009:382: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu /
NK005(ca)009:383: bar pa gnyis kyis kha t+w+aam ka dang thod pa khrag gis gang ba /
NK005(ca)009:384: tha ma gnyis kyis thong ba'i rnge'u chung dang /
NK005(ca)009:385: rgyu ma'i zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK005(ca)009:386: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis rol pa /
NK005(ca)009:387: thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
NK005(ca)009:388: thod rlon gyi do shal dang /
NK005(ca)009:389: thod tshal sbrul rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK005(ca)009:390: zhing lpags dang glang po che'i ko bas stod g.yogs shing /
NK005(ca)009:391: stags lpags kyi sham thabs grol ba /
NK005(ca)009:392: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan ma sogs dur khrod chen po'i chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)009:393: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sngo skya g.yas dril
NK005(ca)009:394: bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon dung khrag
NK005(ca)009:395: stob pa / gcer bu lang tsho rgyas pa'i 'jo sgeg can /
NK005(ca)009:396: zhabs g.yas brkyang ba'i rol pas yab dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba /
NK005(ca)009:397: ye shes kyi me dpung rab tu 'bar zhing 'khrug pa'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:399: rang gi spyi bor dkar po /
NK005(ca)009:401: thugs kar h+aum mthing ga rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK005(ca)009:404: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sad par byas /
NK005(ca)009:407: lus thams cad khyab pas khro chung smug nag tshon gang bas dkrigs shing gtams par bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:408: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)009:409: de bzhin du mgrin pa'i +aamhls 'od zer 'phros /
NK005(ca)009:410: ngag gi zhen de bzhin gshegs pa gsung gi byin
NK005(ca)009:411: rlabs bsdus nas +aahl thim pa 'od du 'bar ba
NK005(ca)009:412: las ljags rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i rtse mor pad+ma'i
NK005(ca)009:413: lte bar +aamhl ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar
NK005(ca)009:414: bsam zhing / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros /
NK005(ca)009:416: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sad par byas /
NK005(ca)009:417: thugs kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas h+aum la thim pa 'od du 'bar ba las /
NK005(ca)009:418: tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang zla gam sgo
NK005(ca)009:419: gcig pa'i nang du nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan la
NK005(ca)009:420: ye shes sems dpa' smug nag tshon gang ba /
NK005(ca)009:421: de'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng du rin po che
NK005(ca)009:422: zur brgyad pa'i nang du phyed nub tsam gyi rdo
NK005(ca)009:423: rje rtse dgu pa'i lte bar h'u yig sngon po
NK005(ca)009:424: 'bar / rin po che'i zur brgyad kyi rtse la
NK005(ca)009:425: ru lu 'bru brgyad ljang dmar spus bris pa tsam
NK005(ca)009:426: klag phyogs su 'khor zhing 'od zer 'phro bar bsam
NK005(ca)009:427: 'bar / la / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:428: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)009:429: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK005(ca)009:430: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)009:431: phyag rgya chen por mngon rdzogs nas //
NK005(ca)009:432: sku gsung thugs su rang dbang bskur //
NK005(ca)009:433: zhes brjod cing nga rgyal bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:434: gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:435: bdag gi thugs ka'i h+aum las h'u ring gis gyen
NK005(ca)009:436: du drangs pa sna'i rlung dang lhan cig tu srog
NK005(ca)009:437: gi lam nas thon te sna rtser h+aum gi gzugs
NK005(ca)009:440: de las 'od zer 'phros nas sangs rgyas thams cad rjes su bskul bas gcig tu gyur /
NK005(ca)009:441: sam ha ra na h+aum gis bsdus pas sna rtse'i
NK005(ca)009:442: h+aum la 'dus pa dbugs dang lhan cig srog gi
NK005(ca)009:443: lam nas snying ga'i h+aum la zhugs /
NK005(ca)009:444: de las h+aum phra mo zhig byung ba rlung dang
NK005(ca)009:445: sbyar nas las su rung ba dung khang nas zhugs
NK005(ca)009:446: te tshangs pa'i sgor thon pa nyi ma'i gdan la
NK005(ca)009:447: gnas par gyur / de las dpa' bo 'bru lnga 'phros pa rin po che'i khang bu lngar gyur /
NK005(ca)009:448: slar yang h+aum las h+aum yig bzhi 'phros pa spyi bo'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir gnas par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)009:449: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK005(ca)009:450: ma h+aa sh+aunya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)009:451: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na sa ma t+aa pra t+y+aa bek+shana kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na zhes brjod cing /
NK005(ca)009:453: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK005(ca)009:454: phung po lnga sangs rgyas lngar gnas bsgyur nas /
NK005(ca)009:455: khrag 'thung rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:457: rgyu snyoms 'jug gi sbyor ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:460: rang gi thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum chad pa yum gyi mkha' la spros /
NK005(ca)009:461: tha mal gyi 'dzin rtog sbyangs nas 'od du zhu /
NK005(ca)009:462: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he pad+ma d+ha ra tsan+d+ra am /
NK005(ca)009:464: mkha' zla gam dmar po ling tshe dgu par gyur
NK005(ca)009:465: pa'i dbus su pad+ma 'dam ma bzhi pa'i lte bar
NK005(ca)009:466: zla ba la am dmar pos mtshan par bsam /
NK005(ca)009:467: yum gyi thugs ka nas yi ge h+aum chad pa yab kyi gsang gnas su spros /
NK005(ca)009:472: gsang ba rdo rje rtse lnga pa nor bu'i sked
NK005(ca)009:473: bskor can gyi rtse mor nyi ma la dkar pos
NK005(ca)009:475: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)009:478: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK005(ca)009:479: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis drags 'khyud sbyar nas mnyes par byas te /
NK005(ca)009:481: zhes snyoms par zhugs pas bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong bar byas /
NK005(ca)009:482: bde ba'i 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes shing bskul /
NK005(ca)009:483: sems can thams cad kyi dri ma sbyangs /
NK005(ca)009:485: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba rdo rje'i lam
NK005(ca)009:486: nas yum gyi pad+mora spros pa yi ge ha brgyad
NK005(ca)009:487: du gyur / de las so so'i phyag mtshan brgyad du gyur pa badz+ra goo r+ai ha /
NK005(ca)009:488: zhes sogs brjod pa'i sngags kyis sgra gdangs kyis sku
NK005(ca)009:489: phra mor gyur nas mdun gyi nam mkhar 'thon par
NK005(ca)009:490: bsam zhing / yang na mkha' las ha brgya po
NK005(ca)009:491: so so'i gdan la spros pa rang sngags kyis skur
NK005(ca)009:494: nam mkha'i lha rnams sku brtas par byas te zla gam brgyad kyi gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:496: shar du dkar mo mthing ga g.yas zhing dbyug 'phyar zhing g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)009:498: lhor rkun mo ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'i rtse mo gtso bo'i thugs kar gtod pa /
NK005(ca)009:500: nub tu spos mo dmar mo g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)009:502: byang du rmongs mo mthing nag g.yas rdo rje rgya gram 'phyar zhing /
NK005(ca)009:503: g.yon zhing chung gi dbyug pa g.yob pa /
NK005(ca)009:505: shar lhor rgan byed ma dmar ser g.yon zhing chung
NK005(ca)009:506: bzung ba'i rgyu ma g.yas pas 'dren cing stob pa
NK005(ca)009:508: lho nub tu thal byed ma ljang nag g.yas pa'i
NK005(ca)009:509: rdo rjes g.yon gyi dung khrag dkrug cing gsol ba
NK005(ca)009:511: nub byang du ma tshogs ma mthing nag phyag gnyis kyi zhing bzung nas snying za ba /
NK005(ca)009:513: byang shar du dur khrod ma ser skya g.yon zhing
NK005(ca)009:514: chung bzung ba'i mgo bo g.yas pas bcad nas za
NK005(ca)009:515: ba / de thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ma /
NK005(ca)009:518: gcer bu dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK005(ca)009:519: g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis zhing gi stan la rol pa /
NK005(ca)009:520: thams cad kyi thugs kar nyi ma la gnas pa'i
NK005(ca)009:521: rin po che zur brgyad pa'i lte bar ha yig
NK005(ca)009:522: la ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK005(ca)009:523: de ltar zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung khams skye
NK005(ca)009:524: mched kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad zag pa med
NK005(ca)009:525: pa lha'i rang bzhin du ye nas rnam par dag
NK005(ca)009:527: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK005(ca)009:528: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba /
NK005(ca)009:537: bstim zhing gzi byin bskyed pa dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)009:539: snying ga'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas chos
NK005(ca)009:540: dbyings skye ba med pa'i ngang las gzugs sku ye
NK005(ca)009:541: shes kyi 'khor lor bzhengs par bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:542: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes se gol dpung mgor bsnol mar gdab cing /
NK005(ca)009:544: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul nas //
NK005(ca)009:546: sems can don slad dam tshig dgongs //
NK005(ca)009:547: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:549: thod phreng gi rgya dpral bar bcings te /
NK005(ca)009:550: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a gat+ta ya /
NK005(ca)009:561: sh+r+ai ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu dra /
NK005(ca)009:563: ces pas snyan gsan dbab bo //
NK005(ca)009:566: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK005(ca)009:567: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs he ru ka /
NK005(ca)009:568: chos sku zhi ba'i ngang las kyang //
NK005(ca)009:569: gzugs sku 'jigs tshul bstan du gsol //
NK005(ca)009:570: thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)009:571: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:572: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal dang ldan //
NK005(ca)009:573: tshogs kyi slob dpon gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:574: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK005(ca)009:575: sprul pa'i tshogs kyang gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:576: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan dzahh+aum bam hoh ru
NK005(ca)009:577: lu ru lu dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK005(ca)009:579: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka e h+ye dri
NK005(ca)009:580: sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK005(ca)009:581: / e badz+ra +aa ra li hoh h+r+aim h+r+aim h+r+aim /
NK005(ca)009:582: zhes brjod cing thal mo lan gsum du brdabs pas spyan drangs te /
NK005(ca)009:583: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK005(ca)009:584: me ri 'dabs 'byar tsam du bzhugs par bsam mo
NK005(ca)009:588: 'gro ba ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)009:589: don gyi dbang du dgongs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:592: thod phreng gi phyag rgya smin mtshams su bcings te /
NK005(ca)009:593: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu dra /
NK005(ca)009:595: sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:596: dzahh+aum bam hohsh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam /
NK005(ca)009:600: ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig pa la bye
NK005(ca)009:601: ma la mar thim pa bzhin bstim nas gzi byin
NK005(ca)009:603: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba /
NK005(ca)009:606: zil gyis mnan pa dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)009:608: sor mo snying gar bsnol ba las mthe bong so sor sgrengs te /
NK005(ca)009:609: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya hoh sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu dra /
NK005(ca)009:611: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)009:613: dngos grub ma thob kyi bar de srid du brtan par bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:615: mche ba'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK005(ca)009:616: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa ma ya dush+tam /
NK005(ca)009:617: a pa s+t+wam pa ka h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:619: gdug byed thams cad zhal du 'dren pa'i phrin las lhun gyis grub pa bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:621: thod pa tshar gsum gyi phyag rgya bstan te /
NK005(ca)009:622: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)009:623: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya hoh badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya sa ma ya phata /
NK005(ca)009:625: dam las mi 'da' bar sgrub po'i re ba bskong bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:627: khyung gshog gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK005(ca)009:628: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam /
NK005(ca)009:637: pra ti stam+b+ha ka ya h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:639: rdo rje'i gshog bar nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK005(ca)009:640: 'phros pas 'khor rnams zil gyis mnan cing dbang du
NK005(ca)009:643: gdul bya snying po'i phyag dang /
NK005(ca)009:644: rtogs pa don gyi phyag gnyis nas /
NK005(ca)009:646: rgyas 'debs ma'i phyag rgya mda' gzhu 'gengs tshul byas la /
NK005(ca)009:647: sh+r+ai badz+ra ka ra mu ka shwa ra y+aa ya na mah zhes pas /
NK005(ca)009:648: gtso bo yab yum gyi sku gsal bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:649: rmongs byed ma'i 'khyud rgya bcas la /
NK005(ca)009:650: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga sa ma y+aa ya na mah zhes pas /
NK005(ca)009:651: gtso bo yab yum rol ba'i bde bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:652: za byed ma'i kha t+w+aam gyi rgya bstan la /
NK005(ca)009:653: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra tsa la y+aa ya na mah zhes pas /
NK005(ca)009:654: yab yum rol pa'i byang sems kyi 'od kyis dregs
NK005(ca)009:655: pa thams cad zil gyis mnan nas bka' nod par
NK005(ca)009:656: bsam mo // tshe 'phel ma'i dril bu'i rgya bcas la /
NK005(ca)009:657: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra tsa la y+aa ya na mah zhes pas /
NK005(ca)009:658: gtso bo'i sems sprin h+aum du gyur pa las spro
NK005(ca)009:659: bsdu'i sbyor bas ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba
NK005(ca)009:660: dril bu thogs par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)009:661: lha mo bzhi yang gtso bo la thim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:663: rang nyid gtso bo'i thugs ka nas he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i rnam par thon te /
NK005(ca)009:664: shar sgor 'khod pas phyag byed par mos la /
NK005(ca)009:666: dbyings nyid rang bzhin rnam par dag pa las //
NK005(ca)009:667: thugs rje'i dbang gis sprul pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NK005(ca)009:668: dpal chen khrag 'thung goo r+ai ma brgyad sogs //
NK005(ca)009:669: rang snang lha tshogs rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:670: a ti pu hoh sarba ta th+aa ga ta ban+d+ha nam ka ro y+aa mi /
NK005(ca)009:672: pra ti pu hoh zhes phyag byas pas /
NK005(ca)009:673: bdag gi sgo gsum dang dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs dbyer med du rtogs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:677: sna tshogs ro ldan gyis mchod pa dang gsum /
NK005(ca)009:686: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)009:687: dpal chen khrag 'thung phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)009:688: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK005(ca)009:689: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK005(ca)009:690: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK005(ca)009:691: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon //
NK005(ca)009:692: dpal chen ye shes thabs kyi rgya //
NK005(ca)009:693: shes rab dbyings ma'i phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)009:694: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK005(ca)009:695: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la brten //
NK005(ca)009:696: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK005(ca)009:697: krod+h+ai shwa r+ai dbyings kyi rgya //
NK005(ca)009:698: dpal chen khrag 'thung yab yum gnyis //
NK005(ca)009:699: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:700: mchod bzhes dam skongs dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)009:701: gnas kyi ma mo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)009:702: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK005(ca)009:703: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK005(ca)009:704: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK005(ca)009:705: be ta byis sha rdor 'phyar nag /
NK005(ca)009:708: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK005(ca)009:710: goo r+ai khro mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK005(ca)009:711: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes zhes brjod cing gar bsgyur bas
NK005(ca)009:712: phyag rgya ye shes kyi rol mos nam mkha' gang
NK005(ca)009:713: bar bsam mo // gnyis pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:715: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK005(ca)009:716: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK005(ca)009:717: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK005(ca)009:718: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK005(ca)009:719: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK005(ca)009:720: khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK005(ca)009:721: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)009:723: spyod yul gyi dngos po thams cad rtog bral kun tu bzang po'i rol par dbul lo //
NK005(ca)009:726: ar+g+ham me tog bdug spos dang //
NK005(ca)009:727: mar me dri chab bshos dang sgra //
NK005(ca)009:728: phyi nang gsang bar sbyar ba rnams //
NK005(ca)009:729: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la dbul //
NK005(ca)009:730: pa na pem sogs kyis mchod sprin spros te /
NK005(ca)009:732: srid rtsa dbyings su shar ba'i mchod sprin 'di //
NK005(ca)009:733: de nyid ma bcos yum gyi thig ler shar //
NK005(ca)009:734: chags yul bde bas 'od phung dmar la 'khyil //
NK005(ca)009:735: nyon mongs dbyings su bstim phyir ar+g+ham bzhes //
NK005(ca)009:736: rak+ta tsit+ta sho d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)009:737: 'byung lnga'i dbyings las ye shes bcud shar ba //
NK005(ca)009:738: snang srid mdangs bsdus rang bzhin me tog gsal //
NK005(ca)009:739: gnyis med ngang las kha dog cir yang snang //
NK005(ca)009:740: 'bras bu bcud ldan me tog 'od phung 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:741: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK005(ca)009:742: ma bcos rang byung dam rdzas spos mchog 'di //
NK005(ca)009:743: kha dog dbyibs gsal dbang mchog tshim byed pa'i //
NK005(ca)009:744: stong gsum dri bsung dag pa'i bdug spos 'di //
NK005(ca)009:745: 'bar ba'i shangs su mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK005(ca)009:746: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK005(ca)009:747: snod bcud gnyis med yab yum dag pa las //
NK005(ca)009:748: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes mer shar nas //
NK005(ca)009:749: mtha' dbus med par gsal ba'i 'od 'bar 'di //
NK005(ca)009:750: 'khor ba'i mun khang gzhom phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:751: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih gnyis med mkha' dbyings dag pa'i pho brang du //
NK005(ca)009:752: nyon mongs skyon bral dag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK005(ca)009:753: cir yang 'char phyir dri yi 'od phung 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:754: zhal gyi dbyings su thim nas mnyes gyur cig /
NK005(ca)009:755: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK005(ca)009:756: nam mkha' kun bzang dbyings nas cir yang 'byung //
NK005(ca)009:757: 'byung ba'i 'bras bu 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga //
NK005(ca)009:758: lha bshos yid bzhin rin chen yo byad 'di //
NK005(ca)009:759: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du thim par bzhes //
NK005(ca)009:760: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga nee wi t+y+ae kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:761: sgra yi dngos por snang ba yang //
NK005(ca)009:762: yod pa ma yin shin tu grags //
NK005(ca)009:763: sgra yis rab tu tshim 'gyur yang //
NK005(ca)009:764: sgra nyid rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK005(ca)009:765: sgra byung ye shes mchod par 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:766: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)009:767: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga g+airti h+r+aih zhes sam bsdu na /
NK005(ca)009:768: mchod sprin spro ba'i sngags kyi mjug tu so so'i
NK005(ca)009:769: mchod sngags rnams btags pa tsam gyis kyang rung ngo
NK005(ca)009:770: // gang ltar kyang mchod pa rnams pa bdun po
NK005(ca)009:771: phyi nang gsang ba'i sprin chen por spros te phul
NK005(ca)009:772: // bar bsam mo // bzhi pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:773: bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po dri ma med pa lta bur sbar la /
NK005(ca)009:776: zhes gsum mam lnga bzlas la /
NK005(ca)009:778: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK005(ca)009:779: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK005(ca)009:780: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK005(ca)009:781: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK005(ca)009:782: rgyud drug sems can kun sgrol phyir //
NK005(ca)009:783: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK005(ca)009:784: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)009:785: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyi //
NK005(ca)009:786: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)009:787: 'di ni sngon gyi tha tshig go //
NK005(ca)009:788: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK005(ca)009:789: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK005(ca)009:790: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK005(ca)009:791: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)009:792: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hohkha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:795: ston pa kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK005(ca)009:796: dga' rab rdo rje 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang //
NK005(ca)009:797: ro langs bde ba sangs rgyas gsang ba la //
NK005(ca)009:798: sman mchod 'bul lo mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)009:799: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hokha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:800: bal po h+aum mdzad pad+ma sam b+ha wa //
NK005(ca)009:801: nam mkha'i snying po ye shes gzhon nu dang //
NK005(ca)009:802: dpal gyi ye shes gnubs chen sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)009:803: sman mchod sarba ye dbang kalpo dbang gi gtsug tor dang //
NK005(ca)009:804: so ston rgyal po chos seng r+aa dza 'bar //
NK005(ca)009:805: chos ye bstan pa rgyal tsha mgon po la //
NK005(ca)009:806: sman mchod sarba pad+ma rgyal mtshan bde gshegs pad 'byung dang //
NK005(ca)009:807: rat+na sh+r+ai chos mchog chos ldan zhabs //
NK005(ca)009:808: gsang bdag se ston dpal 'bum mgon bzang la //
NK005(ca)009:809: sman mchod sarba rin chen rgyal mtshan mgon po zla ba dang //
NK005(ca)009:810: ngag dbang rdo rje dpal ldan bkra shis zhabs //
NK005(ca)009:811: legs grub tshe ring rdo rje chos dbyings la //
NK005(ca)009:812: sman mchod sarba gter bdag gling pa 'gyur med rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK005(ca)009:813: rin chen rnam rgyal o rgyan bstan 'dzin rje //
NK005(ca)009:814: phrin las rnam rgyal phrin las chos kyi sgron //
NK005(ca)009:815: sman mchod sarba sangs rgyas kun dga' bstan 'dzin nor bu'i sde //
NK005(ca)009:816: rigs bdag gyur med phan bde'i 'od zer zhabs //
NK005(ca)009:817: brgyud srol kun 'dus rtsa ba'i bla ma la //
NK005(ca)009:818: sman mchod sarba rab 'byams dkyil 'khor kun gyi dbang phyug che //
NK005(ca)009:819: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog 'khor lo'i lha //
NK005(ca)009:820: d+aa ki chos skyong rgya mtsho'i tshogs bcas la //
NK005(ca)009:821: sman mchod sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham sman mchod brgyud 'debs ltar kha bsgyur dz+ny+aa nas so //
NK005(ca)009:823: zhes mtheb srin nyi zla'i ga'usa bdud rtsi phul ba
NK005(ca)009:824: lha rnams kyi ljags kyi dbang pos blangs te dgyes
NK005(ca)009:826: mthar dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:827: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin
NK005(ca)009:828: rlabs bdud rtsi'i steng du +aahh+aum gi ngo bor gnas
NK005(ca)009:830: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje la //
NK005(ca)009:831: rdo rje can gyi h+aum bsgoms te //
NK005(ca)009:832: mthe bong dang ni srin lag rtses //
NK005(ca)009:833: myang pas byang chub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK005(ca)009:834: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK005(ca)009:835: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:836: zhes gu h+ya lag gi phyag rgyas 'bru gsum rim
NK005(ca)009:837: par blangs pa lce'i h+aum gis drangs nas gnas gsum
NK005(ca)009:838: gyi 'bru gsum dang ro gcig tu gyur pas sku
NK005(ca)009:839: gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:841: rin po che 'bar ba'i rgya bcas te /
NK005(ca)009:843: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK005(ca)009:844: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam pa lnga //
NK005(ca)009:845: mnyam nyid skye ba med dbyings las //
NK005(ca)009:846: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:847: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:848: zhes gtor ma 'dod yon gyi sprin du spros pas dgyes shing tshim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:849: slar yang bdud rtsi gtor mar bran la /
NK005(ca)009:850: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:852: bdud rtsi ro brgya dang ldan pa lha rnams kyis gsol bar bsam pa ste /
NK005(ca)009:853: rjes 'brel gsang ba sman gyi mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)009:854: gnyis pa khyad par du mchod pa stob pa ni gar rgya las dung chen gyi rgya bcas te /
NK005(ca)009:856: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK005(ca)009:857: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK005(ca)009:858: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK005(ca)009:859: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK005(ca)009:860: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas /
NK005(ca)009:861: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK005(ca)009:863: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:864: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka i dam /
NK005(ca)009:869: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai b+aan kha kha /
NK005(ca)009:871: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra +aa be sha ya /
NK005(ca)009:875: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai b+aan kha kha kha /
NK005(ca)009:876: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:877: zhes stob pas mchod pa thams cad sku la thim zhing zhal du gsol bar bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:878: gsum pa ro ldan gyi mchod pa las /
NK005(ca)009:881: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK005(ca)009:882: khams gsum ma lus bsgral bar bya //
NK005(ca)009:883: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)009:884: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK005(ca)009:885: dzahh+aum bam hohsh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK005(ca)009:893: sngar bstabs pa de dag gtso 'khor rnams kyis rol par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:896: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK005(ca)009:897: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bas bcings pa yi //
NK005(ca)009:898: dmar chen bskyil ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK005(ca)009:900: ma rungs 'dod la ma chags shing //
NK005(ca)009:901: dam tshig la sdang dgra chen rnams //
NK005(ca)009:902: thugs rje byang sems ldan pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:903: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK005(ca)009:904: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK005(ca)009:909: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK005(ca)009:910: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK005(ca)009:912: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:914: 'khor ba'i chags rtog gi rak+ta la rol pas dgyes
NK005(ca)009:915: pa bskyed de thams cad sangs rgyas par bsam mo
NK005(ca)009:916: // mchod pa'i rim pa de dag kyang /
NK005(ca)009:917: tshul rig cing goms pas mdo rgyas ci rigs su bstan par bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:919: d+harma k+aa ya na mah sam+b+h+yo k+aa ya na mah
NK005(ca)009:920: nirma na k+aa ya na mah dz+ny+aa na pany+tsa k+aa
NK005(ca)009:921: ya na mah k+aa ya w+aak+tsit+ta /
NK005(ca)009:922: gu na ka ma hri da ya na mah sarba ta th+aa ga ta na mo na mah h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:923: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK005(ca)009:924: byams dang snying rjes dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK005(ca)009:925: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK005(ca)009:926: 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)009:927: mi gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa las //
NK005(ca)009:928: bdud 'dul khro bo mchog gi skur sprul pa //
NK005(ca)009:929: thugs rje'i gzi ldan gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul //
NK005(ca)009:930: bcom ldan khro rgyal la yang phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)009:931: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer gnas shing //
NK005(ca)009:932: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)009:933: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ba //
NK005(ca)009:934: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)009:935: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK005(ca)009:936: 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK005(ca)009:937: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK005(ca)009:938: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'di ni sangs rgyus thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)009:939: yang dag yon tan rgya chen te //
NK005(ca)009:940: lan gcig tsam zhig brjod pas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:942: zhes dril bu dang cang te'u'i sgras bskul te /
NK005(ca)009:943: yon tan khyad par can dran pa'i sgo nas bstod do //
NK005(ca)009:947: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)009:949: dbyer gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar dmigs la /
NK005(ca)009:950: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra b+hany+dza dz+ny+aa na man+dala phata dzah zhes dang /
NK005(ca)009:951: gtso 'khor dgu po'i bskyed sngags la /
NK005(ca)009:953: dam tshig gi 'khor lo las ye shes kyi 'khor
NK005(ca)009:954: lo rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye
NK005(ca)009:955: nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:957: bdag mdun gyi gtso bo sems dpa' sum brtsegs sngags phreng dang bcas pa sngar bzhin dang /
NK005(ca)009:958: ma mo brgyad kyi thugs kar b+hany+dza til 'bru tsam
NK005(ca)009:959: re'i steng du ha re re'i mthar yang ru lu
NK005(ca)009:960: 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar gsal ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:961: rang gi lce rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i rtse mor
NK005(ca)009:962: pad+ma'i lte bar +aamhl ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor
NK005(ca)009:963: ba / de dag kyang mar me ltar 'bar zhing gsal ba'i 'od zer 'phro bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:965: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul du 'phros pas /
NK005(ca)009:966: ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK005(ca)009:968: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad 'od zer
NK005(ca)009:969: gyi rnam par bdag la stsal zhing thim par dmigs
NK005(ca)009:970: te / dam ye 'phro 'du ba thag gzengs pa lta bu'i ngang nas /
NK005(ca)009:971: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:972: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)009:973: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:975: de bzhin du 'khor rnams la yang /
NK005(ca)009:976: rang rang gi thugs ka dang 'phro 'du bdag nyid gtso bo las sam /
NK005(ca)009:977: rang spro bsdu byed kyang rung /
NK005(ca)009:978: so so'i sngags la ru lu sbyar bas so //
NK005(ca)009:979: yang na dam ye 'phro 'du dus gcig mgar gyi tsh+wa tsh+wa brdabs pa bzhin nam /
NK005(ca)009:980: ma phye bar yab yum khong brgyud mgal me bskor ba'i tshul du byas kyang rung ste /
NK005(ca)009:982: gtso bor ni spyi 'dzab ru lu kho na bzla zhing /
NK005(ca)009:983: thun mtshams su stong tshigs kyi mchod bstod kyang bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:984: 'di ni sgrub mchod sogs kyi skabs don dang bstun nas snying po tsam du smos kyi /
NK005(ca)009:985: gzhan du dbyangs kyi bye brag dang /
NK005(ca)009:988: 'bru brgyad kyi mtshan nyid kyi tshul du bzla ba rnams te /
NK005(ca)009:990: dam pa snga ma rnams kyis mdzad pa las shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:991: de yang grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa rnams dman 'bring mchog gi dbye bas bshad kyang /
NK005(ca)009:992: nub re tsam la tshad bzung du mi btub pas ci nus bzla ba tsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:993: gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:994: de ltar bzlas brjod bgyis so 'tshal gcig tu bsdus pa mchod pa'i sprin du phul la /
NK005(ca)009:996: sngags tshig bzlas brjod 'phrul po che //
NK005(ca)009:998: phreng bar spel cing bar ma chad //
NK005(ca)009:999: gsal 'dres blo rtog goms pa las //
NK005(ca)009:1000: ting 'dzin cho ga phun sum tshogs //
NK005(ca)009:1001: ma lus gcig tu bsdus nas su //
NK005(ca)009:1002: ye shes lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:1003: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis mnyes mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)009:1004: bdag cag rnams la dgyes par mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1005: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1007: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin mchod pa'i 'od zer 'phros pa /
NK005(ca)009:1008: ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i thugs kar thim pas dgyes pa bskyed /
NK005(ca)009:1009: gtso 'khor thams cad mnyes pa'i 'od zer bsnol mar 'phros pas rjes su chags pa'i rol pa mdzad /
NK005(ca)009:1010: bde ba'i sgras mkha' khyab kyi sangs rgyas thams cad
NK005(ca)009:1011: sku la bsdus nas byang chub sems kyi ngo bor
NK005(ca)009:1012: zhu ba gsang ba'i mkha' la char ltar babs pa
NK005(ca)009:1013: rgya mtshor 'khyil zhing gsal bar gyur pa la //
NK005(ca)009:1014: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)009:1015: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)009:1016: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK005(ca)009:1017: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)009:1018: zhes brjod cing rig pa'i me tog gis bskul bas /
NK005(ca)009:1022: skar mda' 'am nyi zer lta bu 'od zer lnga dang ldan pa grangs med pa 'phros /
NK005(ca)009:1024: ba spu'i sgo nas zhugs pas lus thams cad gang bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)009:1025: mthar ye shes kyi 'khor lo yang /
NK005(ca)009:1026: h'u zhes dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis med
NK005(ca)009:1027: du bstim pas shin tu gsal zhing brtan la gzi
NK005(ca)009:1028: byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:1029: 'di ni man ngag khyad par ba'i phyogs gcig brjod pa yin gyi /
NK005(ca)009:1031: bstod cing bshags pa dang bsdu ba spyi ltar byas kyang rung ngo //
NK005(ca)009:1032: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK005(ca)009:1037: spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor dang lnga'o //
NK005(ca)009:1038: dang po tshogs mchod la'ang lnga las /
NK005(ca)009:1039: dang po bshams shing byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1040: dam rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad rnams bshams nas bdud rtsis bran la /
NK005(ca)009:1041: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ais bsang /
NK005(ca)009:1044: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros /
NK005(ca)009:1045: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas /
NK005(ca)009:1046: dngos 'dzin nyes skyon thams cad bsregs gtor bkrus te stong par gyur /
NK005(ca)009:1047: stong pa'i ngang las h+r+aihls tshogs gzhong rin po che'i snod du /
NK005(ca)009:1048: tshogs rdzas tram las rin po che'i phung por bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:1049: tram rat+na tree lokya s+pha ra na phata /
NK005(ca)009:1051: rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i bdud rtsi 'dod yon drug
NK005(ca)009:1052: gi sprin phung mkha' khyab tu spro bar bsam la
NK005(ca)009:1053: / 'bru gsum lan gsum brjod par byin gyis brlab /
NK005(ca)009:1054: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1056: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK005(ca)009:1057: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK005(ca)009:1058: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK005(ca)009:1059: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas dang //
NK005(ca)009:1060: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)009:1062: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la gshegs //
NK005(ca)009:1063: dza h+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka dri sh+ya
NK005(ca)009:1064: hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wamh badz+ra
NK005(ca)009:1065: +aa ra li hohh+r+aim h+r+aimh zhes pas spyan drangs la
NK005(ca)009:1066: / gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi dang po spyir mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1067: tshad med bzhi las grub pa yi //
NK005(ca)009:1068: spos dang me tog mar me dri //
NK005(ca)009:1069: ye shes bzhi las shar ba yi //
NK005(ca)009:1070: me long phreng ba gling bu gar //
NK005(ca)009:1071: gzugs ni rnam snang mdzad la 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:1072: dri ni rin chen 'byung ldan la //
NK005(ca)009:1073: sgra ni snang ba mtha' yas nyid //
NK005(ca)009:1074: ro ni don yod grub pa ste //
NK005(ca)009:1075: reg ni rdo rje sems dpar 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:1076: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK005(ca)009:1082: gnyis pa bye brag tu mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1083: tshogs phud cha gsum mam bzhir spros te /
NK005(ca)009:1084: dang po g.yas zhal dkar po la dmigs te mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1086: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK005(ca)009:1087: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK005(ca)009:1088: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)009:1089: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK005(ca)009:1090: gar yang sgrub po rnal 'byor las //
NK005(ca)009:1091: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK005(ca)009:1092: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK005(ca)009:1093: m+aam sa la logs ro mchog gsol //
NK005(ca)009:1094: me tog sogs dang tsan+dana dri //
NK005(ca)009:1095: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:1096: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK005(ca)009:1097: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)009:1098: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK005(ca)009:1099: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1100: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK005(ca)009:1106: ba lim ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai m+aam kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:1107: zhes 'dod yon drug gi mchod pas dgyes par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:1108: gnyis pa g.yon zhal la dmigs te bshags pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1110: tshe rabs thog ma med pa tshun chad nas //
NK005(ca)009:1111: da lta'i lus 'di blangs pa yan chad du //
NK005(ca)009:1112: lus kyis sdig byas spyod pa ngan du spyad //
NK005(ca)009:1113: ngag gis tshig 'khyal smra ba ngan du brjod //
NK005(ca)009:1114: sems kyis blo nor log par bsam pa sogs //
NK005(ca)009:1115: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis pa //
NK005(ca)009:1116: bkra ba'i lha tshogs khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK005(ca)009:1117: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK005(ca)009:1118: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1119: mi yi skyon mthong tsam na bar chad rtsom //
NK005(ca)009:1120: nongs shing 'gal 'khrul ci bgyis mthol zhing bshags //
NK005(ca)009:1121: zhes dang yig brgya brjod cing /
NK005(ca)009:1122: tshogs rdzas bdud rtsir phul bas nyams chag dag par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:1123: tha ma zhal dbus ma la dmigs te stob pa bya ba la /
NK005(ca)009:1127: zhal du stob pa dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)009:1129: ling+ga logs su bcas pa med na sngar gyi tshogs
NK005(ca)009:1130: phud tha ma de'i 'dod yon gyi lha mo h+aum
NK005(ca)009:1131: zhes pas rang la bsdus nas mdun du bkod /
NK005(ca)009:1134: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:1135: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1136: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1137: chos can sgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1138: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po badz+ra he ru ka'i
NK005(ca)009:1139: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK005(ca)009:1140: dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK005(ca)009:1141: ma rungs pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur
NK005(ca)009:1142: pa thams cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la
NK005(ca)009:1144: n+ri yam dzahn+ri badz+ra am ku sha dzah tri yam
NK005(ca)009:1145: dzahtri badz+ra a ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes
NK005(ca)009:1146: pas dgug bcings bsdams nas myos par bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:1148: dmigs bya mgon med skyabs bral rnam par 'gyur ba'i tshul du gnas pa la /
NK005(ca)009:1149: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK005(ca)009:1150: mtshon cha sna tshogs pa'i char du phab pa dmigs
NK005(ca)009:1151: bya la phog / dug lnga ye shes lngar sbyangs /
NK005(ca)009:1152: dwangs ma h+aum yig tu gyur pa phur rtses 'og min du spar bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)009:1153: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK005(ca)009:1154: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa la //
NK005(ca)009:1155: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK005(ca)009:1156: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK005(ca)009:1157: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK005(ca)009:1158: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK005(ca)009:1159: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK005(ca)009:1160: rdul du byas nas tshogs la 'bul //
NK005(ca)009:1161: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1162: sarba dush+tam m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:1165: tho bas brdung ba rnams bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:1168: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK005(ca)009:1169: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer brdal ba ltar //
NK005(ca)009:1170: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK005(ca)009:1171: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:1172: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:1173: 'jigs byed rngams stabs brkyang bskum tshul gyis bzhugs //
NK005(ca)009:1174: za byed bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba ste //
NK005(ca)009:1175: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK005(ca)009:1176: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK005(ca)009:1177: khams gsum za bar chas pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK005(ca)009:1178: nyi zla rab tu 'bar ba'i sdang mig gis //
NK005(ca)009:1179: bdud dpung sreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)009:1180: 'byung po'i sha ni zan las zhim //
NK005(ca)009:1181: gti mug mchod pa bla na med //
NK005(ca)009:1182: bla med mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK005(ca)009:1183: sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)009:1184: 'byung po'i khrag ni chang 'dod chags bla med gsung
NK005(ca)009:1185: gi 'byung po'i rus pa mar zhe sdang bla med
NK005(ca)009:1188: kh+aa hi btags nas phul bas log 'dren thams cad rol pas dgyes par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)009:1189: rgyas par byed na don tshan bdun gyi las rim gzhan du bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o /
NK005(ca)009:1190: bzhi pa tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK005(ca)009:1191: las kyi rdo rjes slob dpon la phyag sngon du 'gro bas tshogs rdzas bsnol mar phul la /
NK005(ca)009:1192: gzigs shig mdzes pa dam pa'i chos //
NK005(ca)009:1193: 'di la the tshom byar mi rung //
NK005(ca)009:1194: bram ze khyi dang gdol pa gsum //
NK005(ca)009:1195: rang bzhin gcig tu dgongs la rol //
NK005(ca)009:1198: bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi mchog /
NK005(ca)009:1199: gzung 'dzin dri ma med pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:1200: 'dod chags dri ma dang bral bas //
NK005(ca)009:1201: de kho na nyid bdag cag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)009:1203: 'dus pa gzhan rnams la'ang drangs te /
NK005(ca)009:1204: nang gi sbyin sreg gis rol pa'i mthar /
NK005(ca)009:1205: he ru ka dpal grong khyer du //
NK005(ca)009:1206: tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ba yis //
NK005(ca)009:1207: bdag gzhan 'gro ba ma lus kun //
NK005(ca)009:1210: lnga pa lhag ma'i cho ga la /
NK005(ca)009:1216: lhag ma rnams bsdus pa'i dme gtor mchod pa'i ras ma dang bcas pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1217: sngar zur du bcad pa'i phud lhag rnams 'du byas /
NK005(ca)009:1218: dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du zhing lpags la thal
NK005(ca)009:1219: chen gyi e gru gsum rak+ta'i thig le gsum dang
NK005(ca)009:1220: ldan pa'i khar dme gtor mar me dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)009:1221: bkod la / phud gtor bdud rtsis sbran no //
NK005(ca)009:1223: bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las /
NK005(ca)009:1225: ces brjod pas gtor ma yar gyi gnas bdun gyii lhar bkra lam gyis gsal bar dmigs /
NK005(ca)009:1227: zhes pas gtor ma'i lha tshogs las mchod sprin sna
NK005(ca)009:1228: tshogs su shar bas lha rnams mchod par bsam la
NK005(ca)009:1229: / a li u le t+aa li ta p+aa li damsh+t+aa /
NK005(ca)009:1230: go n+aa roo tri kha ram yo gi n+ai /
NK005(ca)009:1234: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti /
NK005(ca)009:1235: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK005(ca)009:1236: ma h+aa su kha kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:1238: slar yang h+aum ha he phata kyis gtor ma'i lha
NK005(ca)009:1239: rnams rang la bstim nas gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya
NK005(ca)009:1243: zhes brjod pas lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum mthing
NK005(ca)009:1244: nag 'byams klas pa'i gzhal yas khang du bsam la
NK005(ca)009:1246: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK005(ca)009:1247: mkha' 'gro lhag sdud ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK005(ca)009:1248: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1249: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)009:1250: zhes dang rang gi snying ga nas 'dod pa'i rgyal
NK005(ca)009:1251: po spros pas mgron rnams bkug par bsam zhing de'i
NK005(ca)009:1252: rgya bcings te / dzahh+aum bam hoh a gat+ta ya /
NK005(ca)009:1262: badz+ra t+aa ki h+aum dzahdzah zhes spyugs pa'i brda dang bcas te spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)009:1263: he ru ka'i sngags rgyas zil gyis gnod pa sngar bzhin byas la /
NK005(ca)009:1264: rta mgrin gyi rgya bcings te /
NK005(ca)009:1271: badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)009:1275: rigs so so'i tshom bu lngar bzhugs pas gtor ma gsol bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:1276: badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tshe mam ba ling+ta h+aum phata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:1278: bud+d+ha d+aa ki n+ai sogs nas /
NK005(ca)009:1286: ces mchod cing sman raka sbreng ngo //
NK005(ca)009:1287: de nas rang gi lce la rta mgrin yum bzhi
NK005(ca)009:1288: dang rol pa mdzad pa'i byang sems dza gad kyi
NK005(ca)009:1289: kha phru dang ro gcig par mkha' dbyings kyi phyag
NK005(ca)009:1290: rgya las dme gtor du lan gsum dbab cing /
NK005(ca)009:1291: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK005(ca)009:1292: purba bud+d+ha k+she tra k+sho b+ha ka ra h+aum phata
NK005(ca)009:1293: / ces pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK005(ca)009:1294: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aak+tsit+ta swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)009:1296: sngar gyi phyag rgya des gtor ma nas ltos med du blangs la pra brtags te /
NK005(ca)009:1300: mar rtogs pa skye bas gang thob dngos grub tu rol la /
NK005(ca)009:1301: phud dang lhag ma yang bsres nas sman raka sbreng bzhin du /
NK005(ca)009:1304: pa ra pa ti pa ra pa ti /
NK005(ca)009:1306: tra mi mu ti h+aum kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)009:1311: b+h+yo b+h+yo ma ma b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:1312: b+h+yo b+h+yo ma ma b+h+yo b+h+yo dzah tra ka rak+sha si ta tsar sa ma ya b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:1313: tra ga rak+sha tra ga rak+sha ma ma b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:1314: ma ma ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1315: dz+wa la dz+wa la sa ma ya ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:1316: du ne du ne sa ma ya ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)009:1317: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1318: mkha' 'gro ging dang dbang phyug ma //
NK005(ca)009:1319: ma bdun sring bzhi 'bar ma brgyad //
NK005(ca)009:1320: pho nya la sogs lhag sdud tshogs //
NK005(ca)009:1321: dpal gyi pham phabs 'di gsol la //
NK005(ca)009:1322: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1324: hoh lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK005(ca)009:1325: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)009:1326: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK005(ca)009:1327: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas /
NK005(ca)009:1328: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK005(ca)009:1330: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK005(ca)009:1332: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK005(ca)009:1333: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi sdong grogs mdzod /
NK005(ca)009:1334: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK005(ca)009:1335: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:1336: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK005(ca)009:1337: ces bshags shing phrin las bcol /
NK005(ca)009:1338: ya hi gats+tsha sa mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la /
NK005(ca)009:1339: rol mo dang bcas pas gtor ma phyir dor nas man+dala bsdu'o //
NK005(ca)009:1340: gnyis pa brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:1341: nub tha ma la phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma sman phud kyis sbran la /
NK005(ca)009:1345: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re bzhin rin po
NK005(ca)009:1346: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK005(ca)009:1350: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK005(ca)009:1351: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK005(ca)009:1352: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1353: 'dir spyon dam dgongs phrin las mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1354: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK005(ca)009:1355: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK005(ca)009:1356: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK005(ca)009:1357: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1358: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)009:1359: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK005(ca)009:1360: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK005(ca)009:1361: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1362: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK005(ca)009:1363: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK005(ca)009:1365: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK005(ca)009:1366: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:1367: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK005(ca)009:1368: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK005(ca)009:1369: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK005(ca)009:1370: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK005(ca)009:1371: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK005(ca)009:1372: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK005(ca)009:1373: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK005(ca)009:1374: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK005(ca)009:1375: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)009:1384: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs kyis sman gtor rak+tasa kyang mchod cing /
NK005(ca)009:1387: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol nas /
NK005(ca)009:1388: gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK005(ca)009:1389: gsum pa nyer bsdu bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:1390: thun mtshams la 'jug pa'am nyal ba na /
NK005(ca)009:1392: mchod bstod dang bzod gsol ni byas kyang rung /
NK005(ca)009:1394: gang ltar kyang h+aum zhes dgu brtsegs su brjod pas /
NK005(ca)009:1395: rim pa bzhin gzhal yas khang 'od du zhu nas khro mo brgyad la thim /
NK005(ca)009:1396: de gtso bo yab yum la /
NK005(ca)009:1398: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK005(ca)009:1402: de gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du bsdus nas stong
NK005(ca)009:1403: nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i dbyings su bzhag la
NK005(ca)009:1405: nyal ba las langs pa'am spyod lam la 'jug pa na /
NK005(ca)009:1406: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1407: zhes pas dpal chen po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i skur langs la chad mtha' bsal lo //
NK005(ca)009:1408: bzhi pa go cha bgo zhing lus bsrung ba ni /
NK005(ca)009:1409: rang nyid he ru kar langs pa de nyid gsal
NK005(ca)009:1410: zhing gzi byin dang ldan par gyur pa'i lus kyi
NK005(ca)009:1411: cha thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdul phra rab
NK005(ca)009:1412: kyis gtams pas sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK005(ca)009:1415: cis kyang mi phyed mi shigs pa'i //
NK005(ca)009:1416: stong pa'i go cha bla na med //
NK005(ca)009:1417: mtshan ma'i yul kun bcom nas kyang //
NK005(ca)009:1418: thams cad myur du rgyal bar gnas //
NK005(ca)009:1419: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi ya man+d+ham /
NK005(ca)009:1420: zhes gnas lngar rgyas btab la /
NK005(ca)009:1421: ming dang mtshan mar ma grub pas //
NK005(ca)009:1422: mig gnas ma bral 'dus ma byas //
NK005(ca)009:1423: chos kyi dbyings su bsrungs pas na //
NK005(ca)009:1424: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs so //
NK005(ca)009:1425: h+aum su ra ta rak+sha ham /
NK005(ca)009:1426: zhes brjod cing brtan par byas la /
NK005(ca)009:1427: sgrub pa'i thabs 'dir zhugs pa yis //
NK005(ca)009:1428: dge ba bdag gis gang thob pas //
NK005(ca)009:1429: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1430: sku dang ye shes thob par shog /
NK005(ca)009:1431: ces sogs kyis dge ba bla na med pa'i byang
NK005(ca)009:1432: chub tu bsngo zhing bkra shis kyis mtha' brgyan par
NK005(ca)009:1433: bya'o // lnga pa spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK005(ca)009:1434: phyi ltar na snod bcud kyi dngos por snang ba thams cad sku'i dkyil 'khor /
NK005(ca)009:1435: sgra grags pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK005(ca)009:1436: dran rtog thugs chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK005(ca)009:1437: spyod lam thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum las mi 'da' ba'i ngang nas spyad par bya zhing /
NK005(ca)009:1439: rtog tshogs lha'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:1440: gsang ba ltar na skye med /
NK005(ca)009:1442: ris med du shar ba'i chos thams cad sku gsum
NK005(ca)009:1443: du rtogs pa'i ngang la gnas pas spyod lam bskyang
NK005(ca)009:1445: snying ga'i ru lu phra zhing gsal ba la dar
NK005(ca)009:1446: gcig sems ma yengs par bzung ba'i ngang la glod
NK005(ca)009:1448: snang med rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor rim gyis
NK005(ca)009:1449: dwags ma'i h+aum yig n+aa da'i bar du bsdus la
NK005(ca)009:1450: bltar med bsam du med pa'i ngang la bzhag go
NK005(ca)009:1451: // 'dir zhar byung khyad par gyi nges pa cung zad bshad na /
NK005(ca)009:1452: spyir nges rdzogs kyi sgrub pa'i dbang du zhi ba
NK005(ca)009:1453: la bsnyen pa'i rtags thon nas khro bor bsgyur te
NK005(ca)009:1454: sgrub pa dang / de dang sgo bstun te mos
NK005(ca)009:1455: slob la'ang zhi khro gnas bsgyur gyi phyag len mdzad
NK005(ca)009:1457: 'on kyang mos slob la 'di tsam gyis dgos pa
NK005(ca)009:1458: 'grub cing bya sla bar mthong nas 'di ltar bkod
NK005(ca)009:1459: pa ste / gnas bsgyur la spro na /
NK005(ca)009:1461: mi bskyod spyan gzigs thugs kyi h+aum ring las //
NK005(ca)009:1462: zhi ba las ni khro bor rim gyis bsgyur //
NK005(ca)009:1463: zhes pas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams gtso bo yab la bsdus te /
NK005(ca)009:1464: de nyid bskyed sngags kyis rdo rje sems dpa'i sku phra mo tshon gang bar bsgyur nas /
NK005(ca)009:1466: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka'i h+aum /
NK005(ca)009:1467: he ru ka yi snang glu ni /
NK005(ca)009:1468: h'u ring dbugs kyi rlung bzhi las /
NK005(ca)009:1469: h'u bzhi sngags kyi dgongs pa ni //
NK005(ca)009:1471: khro bo thams cad 'byung bar byed //
NK005(ca)009:1473: sngar bkod pa ltar shes par bya zhing /
NK005(ca)009:1474: bsgom bya'i lha grangs la yang /
NK005(ca)009:1475: zla gam drug cu rtsa brgyad /
NK005(ca)009:1476: de las khro bcu phri ba'i lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1477: bco brgyad pa sogs rgyud rnams las mang du gsungs kyang /
NK005(ca)009:1478: man ngag gi phyag srol rnams su /
NK005(ca)009:1479: lha mang lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1481: zla gam gcig pa rnams la mdzad pa mang ba las /
NK005(ca)009:1482: yang dag grub pa'i don gyi snying po lha dgu yin par gsungs pa ltar 'dir bkod kyi /
NK005(ca)009:1483: gzhan du zla gam gcig pa la mos na /
NK005(ca)009:1484: rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa'i skabs su /
NK005(ca)009:1485: pho brang nang ma zla gam gcig ma'i nang gi re'u mig cha dgu pa'i don du /
NK005(ca)009:1486: lte ba'i zla gam kha sprod dang /
NK005(ca)009:1487: brten pa lha ni gtso bo yab yum kho na bsgoms nas /
NK005(ca)009:1488: g.yas g.yon gyi zhal gnyis dang /
NK005(ca)009:1489: phyag mtshan drug pa ma mo brgyad sbyor te /
NK005(ca)009:1490: rgyu mtshan des kyang don gyi snying po lha dgur 'gyur zhing /
NK005(ca)009:1491: sgrub rdzas bkod pa'i skabs nas kyang /
NK005(ca)009:1492: kham phor ri mo bris pa dgu //
NK005(ca)009:1493: snang ba'i 'od dang bcas pa dgram //
NK005(ca)009:1494: zhes pa'i grangs des kyang lha dgur 'grel pa'i phyogs
NK005(ca)009:1495: gzhung gi zin so dang 'byor zhes mkhas pa chen
NK005(ca)009:1498: rtsa ba'i lha dgu zhes gsal bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK005(ca)009:1505: ti ra'i glo snying 'dren par byas kyang rung ste /
NK005(ca)009:1506: man ngag gis de ltar bkral ba'i khungs gsal por yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK005(ca)009:1507: gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK005(ca)009:1511: tshul rig goms pa'i blo dag gis //
NK005(ca)009:1512: ci rigs su ni brtag par bya //
NK005(ca)009:1514: ston pas bstan pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK005(ca)009:1515: sgom rgyud gsal bar ci nus bya //
NK005(ca)009:1516: zhes pas mtshan med chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i rnal
NK005(ca)009:1517: 'byor dang mtshan bcas lha sku phyag rgya chen po'i
NK005(ca)009:1518: rnal 'byor gsal zhing brtan pa'i sgo nas sngags kyi
NK005(ca)009:1519: bzlas brjod bya ba sogs mnyam gzhag gi rnal 'byor
NK005(ca)009:1520: dang / rjes thob cir snang dag pa rab 'byams su rgyas 'debs pa'i rnal 'byor te /
NK005(ca)009:1521: blo'i rim pas ji tsam nus pa de tsam du 'bad pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK005(ca)009:1523: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK005(ca)009:1524: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK005(ca)009:1525: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK005(ca)009:1526: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)009:1527: ces pas chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas yang dag pa'i dbyings nyid /
NK005(ca)009:1528: blo bur sgrib pa'i sbubs las grol bas dbyings dang
NK005(ca)009:1529: ye shes gnyis med sangs rgyas thams cad kyis nyams
NK005(ca)009:1530: su myong bya'i bde ba chen po mchog tu mi
NK005(ca)009:1531: 'gyur ba sku gsum gyi ngo bor rdzogs pa de
NK005(ca)009:1532: las / dmigs pa med pa'i rtsal snang ye shes
NK005(ca)009:1533: kyi sgyu ma rnam pa thams cad par 'char bas
NK005(ca)009:1534: gzhi 'bras gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid
NK005(ca)009:1535: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub ste /
NK005(ca)009:1536: sa dang pos bsdus pa mthong lam tshe dbang dang
NK005(ca)009:1537: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gang rung gis sgom
NK005(ca)009:1538: lam phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK005(ca)009:1539: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi bar rim pas sam thod rgal du bgrod par 'gyur te /
NK005(ca)009:1540: phung po rdo rje rigs lnga nyid //
NK005(ca)009:1541: nyon mongs ye shes chen por gsal //
NK005(ca)009:1542: bar chad dngos grub nyid du grol //
NK005(ca)009:1543: rdo rje'i sku la 'chi bdag med //
NK005(ca)009:1545: yang dag gsang ba'i thugs mchog la //
NK005(ca)009:1546: sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor dbang phyug rnams //
NK005(ca)009:1547: mi tshe gcig la mngon 'tshang rgya //
NK005(ca)009:1548: lus ma bor bar lha skur 'gyur //
NK005(ca)009:1549: zhes gsungs pa bzhin mngon du 'gyur ba dang /
NK005(ca)009:1550: gzhan yang zhi ba la sogs pa'i phrin las bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)009:1551: ral gri la sogs pa grub pa brgyad de thun
NK005(ca)009:1552: mong gi dngos grub chen po rnams kyang 'grub par
NK005(ca)009:1553: 'gyur ro // dpal ldan he ru ka yi go 'phang mchog /
NK005(ca)009:1554: grub mchog bye bas mngon bgrod zab mo'i lam //
NK005(ca)009:1555: mtha' yas dngos grub kun gyi 'byung gnas che //
NK005(ca)009:1556: lag rtser son 'di skal bzang bsod nams yin //
NK005(ca)009:1557: sngon dus rgya bod kun tu ches dar bas //
NK005(ca)009:1558: grub brnyes rig 'dzin skar tshogs ltar mang yang //
NK005(ca)009:1559: deng dus ming tsam thos pa'ang dkon gyur pa //
NK005(ca)009:1560: ma bzod tshul 'dir brjod la spro bar gyur //
NK005(ca)009:1561: zab rgyas chos kun snying po de bzhin nyid //
NK005(ca)009:1562: tha snyad spros pa'i yul las 'das mod kyang //
NK005(ca)009:1563: brda thabs cho ga'i sbyor ba sna tshogs pas //
NK005(ca)009:1564: lhan skyes gdod ma'i dpa' bo mtshon min nam //
NK005(ca)009:1565: rdo rje bzhi dngos 'gyur med bde chen chos //
NK005(ca)009:1566: mtha' yas 'gro la mi shigs thig le cher //
NK005(ca)009:1567: gnas mod ji srid tshogs gnyis ma goms pa //
NK005(ca)009:1568: de srid mngon du 'gyur ba ga la zhig /
NK005(ca)009:1569: de phyir gdod nas rnam dag yon tan kun //
NK005(ca)009:1570: bde chen thig le chen por rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK005(ca)009:1571: sgrub pa'i thabs tshul 'di las mtshon byas pa'i //
NK005(ca)009:1572: bsod nams bla med byang chub rgyur gyur cig /
NK005(ca)009:1573: dpal he ru ka yang dag thugs kyi sgrub thabs bde chen thig le zhes bya ba 'di ni /
NK005(ca)009:1574: zab mo'i lam 'di nyid ming tsam 'dzin pa yang
NK005(ca)009:1575: dkon par mthong bas 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i sgor 'gyur
NK005(ca)009:1576: bar dmigs te / 'di nyid kyi rgyud rnams dang /
NK005(ca)009:1577: slob dpon chen po h+aum k+aa ras mdzad pa'i sgrub thabs rtsa ba rang 'grel dang bcas pa dang /
NK005(ca)009:1578: pad+ma sam b+ha was rgyas 'grel gyis bkral ba /
NK005(ca)009:1579: lha rje gnubs dang so pa'i man ngag gi bka'
NK005(ca)009:1580: srol phyag bzhes las ji ltar 'byung ba bzhin du
NK005(ca)009:1581: rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes ang+gi ra'i
NK005(ca)009:1582: lo gro zhun gyi nya ba'i tshes dge ba la
NK005(ca)009:1583: o rgyan smin grol gling gi gtsug lag khang du
NK005(ca)009:1584: grub par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni mkhas btsun
NK005(ca)009:1585: bzang po'i dpal gyis mtho ba'i gcung lo ts+aa ba
